  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [x] Foundry\r\n- [X] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\nforge 0.2.0 (4b9cca1 2022-09-03T00:07:15.538624Z)\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nforge coverage  -vvv --report=lcov\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce (works from 0cc0de2ca08c2cd14d5480e8a47c1133147d20dd forward):\r\n\r\n1. `git clone https://github.com/transmissions11/solmate` (or any repo I've tried)\r\n2. `forge coverage  -vvv --report=lcov`\r\n3. Memory growth is unbounded until OOM \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/83933037/188251613-ed5a5e78-146f-4661-adfc-b4cf331ac95d.png)\r\n\r\nHave seen this on both ci (linux) and apple silicon",
